Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
gui_set_legend(25.10)                                    gui_set_legend(25.10)

Name
       gui_set_legend - Specifies the legend setting

Syntax
        gui_set_legend

       [-help]

       [-display_range {x y}]

       [-enable_max_value {true false}]

       [-enable_min_value {true false}]

       [-legend_location {ne nw se sw}]

       [-reset <-display_range|-value_range|-show_legend_on_layout|-legend_lo-
       cation|-enable_min_value|-enable_max_value>]

       [-show_legend_on_layout {true false}]

       -type  {inst_density pin_density timing_map metal_density route_conges-
       tion temperature}

       [-value_range {x y}]

       Specifies the legend setting.

       You can use the gui_set_legend and gui_get_legend commands to  get  the
       snapshot of different density for analysis.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man gui_set_legend

       -display_range {x y}
              Specifies the display range in the {min max} format

       -enable_max_value {true false}
              Enables the max value of the display range.

       -enable_min_value {true false}
              Enables the min value of the display range.

       -legend_location {ne nw se sw}
              Specifies the location of legend.

       -reset <-display_range|-value_range|-show_legend_on_layout|-legend_lo-
       cation|-enable_min_value|-enable_max_value>
              Resets  the  settings  of  the  specified  option,  -reset -dis-
              play_range|-value_range|-show_legend_on_layout|-legend_loca-
              tion<|->enable_min_value<|->enable_max_value. You can reset  all
              options by using  -reset all.

       -show_legend_on_layout {true false}
              Specifies to show the legend on layout.

       -type {inst_density pin_density timing_map  metal_density route_conges-
       tion temperature}}
              Specifies the setting for the specified legend type.

       -value_range {x y}
              Specifies the value range in the {min max} format.

Example
       The following command sets the legend for the inst_density legend type:

       >  gui_set_legend  -type inst_density -display_range {1 0.9} -show_leg-
       end_on_layout true

       The following command gets the current legend setting for the inst_den-
       sity legend type.

       > gui_get_legend -type inst_density

       {display_range {0.9 0.9}} {legend_location  ne}  {show_legend_on_layout
       true} {value_range {0.75 1}}

